<dl id="n36208i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n36" href="#n36208i">N36 (VI.B.29)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n36all.htm#n36208i"> 208(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> 4 As</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[Atheism.]</font> Atheism has its Fundamentals amd it makes no bones about it. The Atheists have set out to combat the Fundamentalists and the ridiculous God idea. They have taken their cue from the enemy &hellip; It is as though the apostles of <mark>4A <font color="green">[The American Association for the Advancement of Atheism]</font></mark> have gone carefully through the catalogue of theology and set down the opposite of every conventional doctrine. <small> Charles W. Ferguson, <a name="CFCT" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CFCT"><cite title="source">The Confusion of Tongues</cite></a> (1928; rpt. May 1929) 431</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
